profile:
Professional moving services at an affordable rate. We also offer packing, trash clean up, installation. Just ask before arrival. 
Moving with your rented truck 75$/h (2H min) 
Moving with my truck 95$/h (3.5 hour min) no travel fees within 30 min of Charlottetown.
piano moving at flat rate 50$ first floor only. We offer deconstruction and removal, basically anything you need moved, installed, cleaned, built, or fixed we do it all. 
Other services : 
-Automotive Repair services 
-snow removal 
-house repairs
-mobile auto repair we come to you

647-998-8457
